title: Chanel Medium Double Flap Bag
description: Chanel medium double flap bag in black patent leather (#14xxxxxx: 2011). Featuring silver-toned hardware, exterior rear pocket and sliding leather-chain woven shoulder straps. The classic CC turn-lock closure on flap opens to an inner flap and a black leather interior with zip and patch pockets. Approximate dimensions: 25cm(L) x 15cm(H) x 6.5cm(D), and 24cm dual shoulder strap drop. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
